headline: UnitedHealth Group Incorporated (UNH) Outlook Strong, Analysts Watch Closely
summary: UnitedHealth Group Incorporated (NYSE:UNH) is among the stocks Wall Street analysts are watching closely. On November 11, Wells Fargo analyst Stephen Baxter reaffirmed a Buy rating on UnitedHealth with a price target of $400. Earlier on November 3, a Barclays analyst had also maintained his Buy rating and a $386 price target. Analysts’ opinion on […]
